videos.headline: Sean Clifford connects with Jahan Dotson for Penn State TD
videos.description: Penn State goes up 7-3 over Auburn as Sean Clifford fires a 4-yard touchdown pass to Jahan Dotson in the back of the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sean Clifford connects with Jahan Dotson for Penn State TD) 2021/09/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tank Bigsby's TD gives Auburn the lead
videos.description: Auburn takes a 10-7 lead as Tank Bigsby barrels his way through traffic and into thee end zone for a 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tank Bigsby's TD gives Auburn the lead) 2021/09/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brenton Strange pulls in Penn State TD catch
videos.description: Sean Clifford links up with Brenton Strange to score a 2-yard touchdown as Penn State retakes the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brenton Strange pulls in Penn State TD catch) 2021/09/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Refs make a mistake, force Penn State to punt on 3rd down
videos.description: Penn State unfortunately loses a possession as the referees make a mistake in telling them they are on fourth down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Refs make a mistake, force Penn State to punt on 3rd down) 2021/09/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tyler Warren leaps for Penn State TD
videos.description: Tyler Warren gets some air as he leaps over a pile to break the plane and score a 2-yard Penn State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tyler Warren leaps for Penn State TD) 2021/09/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tank Bigsby stretches out for Auburn TD
videos.description: Tank Bigsby slips through traffic and stretches out to reach the goal line to score a 6-yard Auburn touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tank Bigsby stretches out for Auburn TD) 2021/09/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's Zakoby McClain in disbelief after targeting call
videos.description: Zakoby McClain falls to the ground in disbelief after he is ejected from the game on a targeting call in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Auburn's Zakoby McClain in disbelief after targeting call) 2021/09/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State increases their lead on Noah Cain's TD run
videos.description: Noah Cain reaches the end zone to score a 3-yard touchdown to push the Penn State lead to 28-20 over Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State increases their lead on Noah Cain's TD run) 2021/09/18 ESHEET
